{"tid":1328272,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺連登仔始終都未做到波台嗰種和而不同嘅概念，一有小小野就分化晒","createTime":"2019-07-18T00:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T02:22:48.000Z","uid":154872,"like":110,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd366dc5a3091185bfb376b78730e261234d975","tid":1328272,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:58:09.000Z","msg":"波台各隊球迷，日夜互片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但玩起膠上嚟都係打成一片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然偶有私怨，但都無礙正常討論<br />\n<br />\n大是大非前更加一致對外，正正係和而不同<br />\n<br />\n據我所知，好多手足都上咗前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而其它台嗰啲，日日夜夜提不分化不割席<br />\n<br />\n但一有小小事(張超雄、林卓廷、陳雲etc)就話人係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌晒全家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有啲冷氣軍師，無兵元帥，喺到日屌夜屌點點點<br />\n<br />\n人地點做你剩係可以比建議<br />\n<br />\n唔係屌人唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇嚟都要入嚟波台做下思想教育"},{"pid":"dfe3ecca181a11116a6285ccb5f95921919d552c","tid":1328272,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:00:06.000Z","msg":"ching有見地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb97a74eaddd9074416fe15242045696375994d","tid":1328272,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:05:20.000Z","msg":"樓主高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d6b9cafa272f03cf28712b1730c28c5eff6b77","tid":1328272,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:06:05.000Z","msg":"